import birriataco from '../../images/image1.jpeg';
import truckmenu from '../../images/truckmenu.png';
import danandjuan from '../../images/danandjuan.jpg';
import fourthpic from '../../images/svg-4.svg';
import menu from '../../images/menutwo.png';
import sixthpic from '../../images/svg-6.svg';

export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'home',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Home',
    headline: 'Traditional Jalisco Style Beef Birria',
    description: 'Sign up for our mailing list to receive notifications on our progress and locations once our food truck is up and running.',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: birriataco,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjTwo = {

    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: true,
    img: truckmenu,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,

    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,

    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjFour = {

    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjFive = {
    id: 'catering',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,

    topLine: 'Catering',
    headline: 'Please fill out the information below',
    description: 'Please fill out the information fields to let us know a little bit more about your catering request and we will get back to you ',
    buttonLabel: 'Place Order',
    imgStart: false,
    img: menu,
    alt: 'Grilling',
    dark: false,
    primary: true,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjSix = {
